    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2442] mt-16 mb-6">The Hidden Cost of "Rented" Expertise</h2>
    <p>
      When you rely on consultants or "key-man" estimators, your business value is capped. If that person leaves or raises their rates, your ability to secure work is paralyzed. This is the definition of scaling friction.
    </p>
    <p>
      Custom software transforms your estimating logic from a set of "expert feelings" into a repeatable, algorithmic process. By codifying your margins, labor rates, and material costs into a dedicated application, you remove the human variable from the mechanical parts of the bid. This allows your team to focus on <strong>strategy</strong>, not data entry.
    </p>

